<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/336465-okay-so-i-have-seen-many-people-say-that">Okay, so I have seen many people say that Madeline is an orphan. I guess I figured she was in a boarding school since she got toys from her &quot;Papa&quot; while in the hospital. Or am I missing something? I ask because I am not familiar with anything Madeline and first just read this to my daughter for her school work.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_336465'><a id="like_count_community_question_336465" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/336465?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F475339.Madeline">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/336465-okay-so-i-have-seen-many-people-say-that">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/336465-okay-so-i-have-seen-many-people-say-that">See all 3 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/61792415-desiree-angeles"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1479795228i/61792415._UY100_CR23,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/61792415-desiree-angeles">Desiree Angeles</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">In the novel, it is highly implied the Madeline as well as the rest of the girls are not orphans but rather students from a Catholic boarding school. <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">In the novel, it is highly implied the Madeline as well as the rest of the girls are not orphans but rather students from a Catholic boarding school. However, this was not the case on the animated films. So that's why many would believe that Madeline and the other girls are living on an orphanage.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

