          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780670445806" href="/book/show/773604.Madeline">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9323164-trina-between-chapters?shelf=2016">2016</a>
