              <span id="reviewTextContainer1743418818" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3595384999429296428">A beautiful library book, enjoyed for its illustrations and most unlikely misbehaving heroine, who was always loved and never punished after her downfalls. I understood fiction at an early age! Lol. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

