            <span class="readable">&ldquo;In an old house in Paris that was covered with vines<br />Lived twelve little girls in two straight lines<br />In two straight lines they broke their bread<br />And brushed their teeth and went to bed.<br />They left the house at half past nine<br />In two straight lines in rain or shine-<br />The smallest one was Madeline.&rdquo;</span>
